<MELItem itemNbr="29-11-04" id="X-BOEING:FTID:81205.787.DDG.CU.MEL.2-29-11-04.1.2-29-11-04">
<Title>Reserve Steering Isolation System</Title>
<DispatchCondition repairInterval="C" nbrInstalled="1" nbrRequired="0" maintIndicator="(M)">
<DispatchConditionRemarks>
<Para>May be inoperative provided reserve steering isolation valve is deactivated open.</Para>
</DispatchConditionRemarks>
<DispatchProcedure>
<MaintenanceProcedure>
<Para>Deactivate reserve steering isolation valve in the open position (AMM DDG 29-11-04).</Para>
<List listType="1.">
<ListItem>
<Para>Open and deactivate the landing gear doors.</Para>
</ListItem>
<ListItem>
<Para>Using a flight deck multi-function display only, open the following circuit breakers and lock with an INOP tag:</Para>
<List listType="A.">
<ListItem>
<Para>HYD ISLN VLV-RSRVD STEERING CLOSE 1</Para>
</ListItem>
<ListItem>
<Para>HYD ISLN VLV-RSRVD STEERING CLOSE 2</Para>
</ListItem>
</List>
</ListItem>
<ListItem>
<Para>Gain access to the reserve steering isolation valve in the left wheel well.</Para>
</ListItem>
<ListItem>
<Para>Deactivate the reserve steering isolation valve in the open position.</Para>
<List listType="A.">
<ListItem>
<Para>Disconnect, cap and stow the reserve steering isolation valve electrical connector.</Para>
</ListItem>
<ListItem>
<Para>Remove the quick release pin from the stow position.</Para>
</ListItem>
<ListItem>
<Para>Set the manual override handle to the OPEN position.</Para>
</ListItem>
<ListItem>
<Para>Insert the quick release pin in the OPEN position.</Para>
</ListItem>
</List>
</ListItem>
<ListItem>
<Para>Close the landing gear doors.</Para>
</ListItem>
</List>
</MaintenanceProcedure>
</DispatchProcedure>
</DispatchCondition>
</MELItem>
</DispatchItems>